def_cn: （话语、主意等）使用过多的,陈腐的,无新意的
def_en: A well-worn expression, remark, or idea has been used so often that it no longer seems to have much meaning or to be interesting.

def_cn: （物品）使用很久的;（衣物）穿旧了的
def_en: A well-worn object or piece of clothing has been worn or used so frequently that it looks rather old and untidy.
